       opn-mod-stp-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Preparazione variabile "inp-mst"                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione preliminare                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-inp-mst              .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo operazione                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "OP"                 to   w-inp-mst-ope          .
